This is the log for ci4miles

Create the app using composer.
composer create-project codeigniter4/appstarter project-root

Add entry to hosts 
127.0.0.1 ci4miles.test

Add entry to httpd.conf
<VirtualHost *:80>
    DocumentRoot "/Applications/MAMP/htdocs/ci4miles/public"
    ServerName ci4miles.test
    ErrorLog "logs/myproject-error_log"
    CustomLog "logs/myproject-access_log" common
</VirtualHost>

Create repository in github